  "title": "Preparation and evaluation of Rice-Straw Compost",
  "abstract": "Rice-straw is an important cattle field in several asian countries even though its quality is low. But in some areas of at least five countries it is burnt. A procedure for rapid composting of rice straw in lots of 10 kg straw in the semi-arid tropics was standardised using Aspergillus awamori, Pseudomonas stritata and bacillus polymyxa...........",
